race.comment: PHAROAH'S PROPHECY (10) is an honest campaigner who is yet to miss the top-four in seven career efforts with all those starts coming around this track. Given a recent trial in preparation for this and looks the one they all have to run down. BOOM SHOT (1) has a handy record over this distance range and gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination. Include in calculations. NO NAME FRANK (9) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim. In the mix. GRAMMAR LAD (4) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on. HEMAN (6) resumes. Got out to a mile last campaign however best results came early in his prep over this trip.
